OL,6,FLast year, the Committee also reversed
OL,7,Fa planned increase to parking charges
OL,8,Fin four areas of Brighton & Hove,
OL,9,Fincluding near the Royal Sussex County
OL,10,FHospital.
OL,12,FBy law, any surplus generated by
OL,13,Fparking fees and charges must be spent
OL,14,Fon provision of public transport
OL,15,Fservices, road safety schemes, air
OL,16,Fquality or environmental improvements.
OL,18,FThis includes helping to maintain our
OL,19,Froads, pavements and cycle routes and
OL,20,Ffixing potholes and other improvements.
